      ****************************************************************          
      * XLRD024 - VERIFIED RECEIPTS AND ADJUSTMENTS                  *          
      *           REPOSITORY LAYOUT (WFT00002-LOD-DAT-TXT)           *          
      * RECORD LENGTH - VARIABLE (DEPENDS ON THE NUMBER OF STORES)   *          
      ****************************************************************          
       01  RD024-RECEIPT-ADJUSTMENT-REC.                                        
           05  RD024-HEADER-DATA.                                               
               10  RD024-ORDER-NUMBER            PIC 9(09).                     
               10  RD024-RCVR-ID                 PIC 9(09).                     
               10  RD024-DC                      PIC 9(04).                     
               10  RD024-SKU                     PIC 9(08).                     
               10  RD024-VRFY-DATE               PIC X(14).                     
               10  RD024-STORE-COUNT             PIC 9(04).                     
               10  FILLER                        PIC X(52).                     
           05  RD024-STORE-DATA OCCURS 1 TO 100 TIMES                           
                                DEPENDING ON RD024-STORE-COUNT                  
                                INDEXED BY RD024-IDX.                           
               10  RD024-STORE                   PIC 9(04).                     
               10  RD024-STORE-QTY               PIC 9(09).                     
               10  RD024-STORE-QTY-SIGN          PIC X(01).                     
